the skull crusher

The Skull Crusher is a hand-tracking experimental game that combines innovative gameplay mechanics with immersive storytelling. Players take on the role of a hero battling the dark magicians cursed army of 100 skulls. Using cutting-edge hand-tracking technology, you aim and destroy enemies with precision and power, creating a deeply engaging experience. The game challenges your skill and reflexes while immersing you in a dark fantasy world.

About visual identity

Visual Identity is a cutting-edge design studio specializing in interactive, award-winning digital experiences. From innovative website design to immersive experiments like The Skull Crusher, we push the boundaries of creativity and technology. With a focus on delivering visually stunning and functionally seamless solutions, we transform ideas into impactful experiences.
